<h3>Reindex the whole site</h3>

<p>
Reindexing the whole site might be useful while upgrading to a CPS
Lucene Catalog from a former zcatalog based instance. Be aware that
this operation might be a bit long depending of the size of your
existing instance.
</p>

<form action="manage_reindex" method="POST">
  <input type="submit" name="reindex" value="Reindex all"/>
</form>

<h3>Optimize the indexes store</h3>

<p>
You can optimize the indexes store here. This is the standard Lucene
optimize feature.
</p>

<form action="manage_optimize" method="POST">
  <input type="submit" name="optimize" value="Optimize indexes"/>
</form>

<p>
You can clear all the indexes from the server store from here.
</p>

<form action="manage_clean" method="POST">
  <input type="submit" name="clean" value="Clean the store"/>
</form>

